{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01M8D16xmhVNAqxBxK1KUMmo","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to generate 10 realistic fake OCR recipe text files with specific requirements:\n\n1. Save to tools/title-loop/input/{RECIPE_TITLE}.generated.21.txt\n2. Filename rules: spaces not hyphens/underscores, preserve Polish diacritics, match title in content\n3. Recipe mix: ~60% English, ~40% Polish, variety of categories\n4. Different from the existing list provided (which is extensive)\n5. Pattern distribution:\n   - 5 files with OCR_CORRUPTION (character corruption, digit for letter, dotless i, hyphenation artifacts, garbage tokens)\n   - 3 files with NARRATIVE (3-7 lines of prose intro)\n   - 2 files with SIMPLE (basic OCR noise, stray numbers, page headers, broken words)\n6. File length: 15-60 lines\n\nLet me create 10 different recipes. I'll pick ones not in the existing list:\n\nEnglish recipes (~6):\n1. Beef Stew with Root Vegetables\n2. Lemon Tart\n3. Mushroom and Barley Risotto\n4. Caprese Sandwich\n5. Berry Fool Dessert\n6. Roasted Chicken with Herbs\n\nPolish recipes (~4):\n1. Żurek z Kielbasą (Sour Rye Soup with Sausage)\n2. Piekarnik (Polish pastry)\n3. Naleśniki z Dżemem (Crepes with Jam)\n4. Kluski Śląskie (Silesian Dumplings)\n\nWait, let me check - some of these might be in the excluded list. Let me be more careful:\n\nExcluded: Piernik Czekoladowy, Żurek, Sernik, Kluski Śląskie z Mięsem, Nalesniki z Serem, etc.\n\n\nI need to refine my selections to avoid the excluded recipes. For English, I'll stick with Beef Stew with Root Vegetables, Lemon Tart, Mushroom and Barley Risotto, Caprese Sandwich, Berry Fool, and Roasted Chicken with Herbs. For Polish, I should use variations like Żurek z Kielbasą (specifying the sausage), Piernik z Orzechami (with nuts instead of chocolate), Naleśniki z Dżemem (with jam), and Oscypek (smoked cheese) to differentiate from the excluded list. and Tomato Sandwich (SIMPLE)\n5. Elderberry Fool (SIMPLE)\n6. Pan-Roasted Chicken with Thyme (CORRUPTION)\n7. Żurek z Kielbasą (CORRUPTION)\n8. Piernik z Orzechami (NARRATIVE)\n9. Naleśniki Słodkie z Dżemem (NARRATIVE)\n10. Kluski Śląskie z Grzybami (CORRUPTION)\n\nI'm organizing these by corruption type: five entries with OCR errors, three with narrative elements, and two straightforward ones. Now I need to generate realistic OCR artifacts for each—things like character substitutions (zero for 'o'), smudged letters, and misaligned text that would naturally occur during scanning.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":15911,"cache_read_input_tokens":65286,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":15911},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"926db9e7-9037-44e8-846b-5b4fe7c8d30b","uuid":"efacfc5f-ed3e-466e-9fa0-3ae0713a8d1a"}
