{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01WWVtWkQaD9bgNQwHBL4TRu","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01V1oiWfgh7mx3yMZmiJ3Lw4","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Barley and Mushroom Pilaf.generated.21.txt","content":"BARLEY AND MUSHROOM PILAF\n\nEvery autumn, as the harvest winds down, home cooks throughout Eastern Europe turn to hearty grain dishes\nthat stretch seasonal mushrooms and root vegetables. This pilaf is inspired by traditional Polish and\nLithuanian autumn preparations, when wild mushrooms are plentiful in forest markets. The earthy barley\nabsorbs the deep umami of sautéed mushrooms, while warming spices like caraway and thyme tie everything\ntogether. Serve it as a main course with pickled vegetables and sour cream, or as a generous side dish\nalongside roasted meats. This dish is best made a day ahead—the flavors deepen overnight.\n\nServes 6 | Prep: 15 min | Cook: 45 min\n\nINGREDIENTS\n\n1 cup pearl barley\n3 cups vegetable or chicken broth\n½ lb mixed mushrooms, sliced\n1 large onion, diced\n4 cloves garlic, minced\n2 tbsp butter\n2 tbsp olive oil\n1 tsp caraway seeds\n1 tsp fresh thyme\n½ cup sour cream (optional, for serving)\nSalt & pepper to taste\n2 bay leaves\nFresh parsley for garnish\n\nMETHOD\n\nHeat butter and oil in large pot over medium heat.\nAdd diced onion, sauté until softened, about 5 minutes.\nAdd sliced mushrooms, cook until they release their liquid, 8-10 minutes.\nAdd minced garlic and caraway seeds, stir for 1 minute.\nAdd pearl barley, toast for 2-3 minutes, stirring constantly.\nPour in broth and add bay leaves.\nBring to a boil, then reduce heat and simmer covered for 35-40 minutes.\nBarley should be tender and liquid mostly absorbed.\nSeason with salt, pepper, and fresh thyme.\nRemove bay leaves.\nServe hot, garnish with fresh parsley and dollop of sour cream if desired.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":719,"cache_read_input_tokens":83034,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":719},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"926db9e7-9037-44e8-846b-5b4fe7c8d30b","uuid":"29ce3ca2-b40b-4a30-8152-8c1ae899ddf9"}
